Albino's voice cut through the tense silence, cold and authoritative. "You," he said, his tone brooking no argument. "Unseal the capsule.” 

For good measure, he reached for his fear-inducing ability, staring directly into the man’s eyes as the wave of fear that swept over him suffused his body, causing him to lose control of all his neural functions even as Albino swiftly withdrew the charge.

The man swallowed hard, his hands trembling as he reached for the controls. For a brief moment, he hesitated, his gaze flickering with uncertainty. But then, with a resigned sigh, he pressed the necessary buttons, his actions driven by the stark realization of the dire consequences of defying Albino's command.
